---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="bg-slate-50 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">

      <!-- Botón de regreso -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <a href="/casos"
          class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 hover:text-brand transition-colors">
          <span aria-hidden="true" class="mr-2">&larr;</span> Back to Case Studies
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Cabecera del Caso -->
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-x-4 text-xs mb-6">
          <span class="text-slate-500">2024-2025</span>
          <span
            class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1.5 font-medium text-brand ring-1 ring-slate-200 uppercase tracking-wider text-[10px]">Travel
            & AI</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-950 sm:text-6xl mb-6 text-balance">Scaling Growth
          through Motion & Systems</h1>
        <p class="text-xl leading-8 text-slate-600">Leading cross-platform experiences for web and mobile. Contributed
          to $14.9M GP and 1.48M installs by surpassing annual targets by 148%.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Metadatos (Rol, Empresa, etc) -->
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-12 grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 border-y border-slate-200 py-8 sm:grid-cols-4">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Client</p>
          <p class="mt-2 font-semibold text-slate-900">Expedia Group</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Role</p>
          <p class="mt-2 font-semibold text-slate-900">Product Designer</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Timeline</p>
          <p class="mt-2 font-semibold text-slate-900">12 Months</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Platform</p>
          <p class="mt-2 font-semibold text-slate-900">iOS, Android, Web</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Imagen Hero -->
      <div class="mt-16 overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-900/10">
        <img src="/DestinationDecoderExp.svg" alt="Project Hero"
          class="w-full h-[400px] sm:h-[600px] object-cover bg-white" />
      </div>

      <!-- Contenido del Caso de Estudio -->
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-20 prose prose-lg prose-slate text-slate-700">
        <span class="font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-brand text-sm mb-4 block">About Project</span>
        <p>For 1y 4m, I was part of the Growth and Retention team at Expedia Group as a Product Designer. In this
          multidisciplinary role, I collaborated closely with Researchers, PMs, Marketing, and Content Designers to
          drive user growth and retention across the global platforms of Expedia, Hotels.com, and VRBO (apps and web
          portals).

          My work spanned various key verticals, including the design of flows and interfaces for referral programs,
          experiences for sharing trips, flights, stays, and activities, the strategic implementation of app download
          banners, AI-powered personalization for user profiles, Destination Decoder (an AI-driven destination discovery
          tool), and the conceptualization of an AI Agent.</p>

        <span class="font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-brand text-sm mb-4 block">Challenges</span>
        <p>Navigating a vast global design system across multiple brands and platforms (Expedia, Hotels.com, VRBO). Designing for a diverse global audience. Ensuring alignment and clear communication across numerous design teams in a fast-paced environment. Pioneering UX solutions for novel AI features without established precedents, which required pushing the boundaries of Figma to create interactive prototypes for user testing and developing custom illustrations, iconography, and animations for key app and web interactions.</p>

        <span class="font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-brand text-sm mb-4 block">Achievements</span>
        <p>Designed and launched globally relevant features, significantly impacting user acquisition and revenue. 
Significant Install Growth & Revenue Generation: Contributed to over 1.6 million installs and over $6.8 million in Gross Profit (GP) across various sharing and app download initiatives.
Exceptional Growth in Sharing & Referrals (2024): By June 2024, projects in sharing and Refer a Friend generated 1.488 million installs, resulting in $14.9 million in Gross Profit, exceeding the annual goal by over 148%.
Proven Uplift in Key Metrics: Achieved up to a 240% uplift in installs with specific banner implementations and conclusive increases in Owned Install Rate for EG share sheets.</p>

        <figure class="my-10">
          <img src="/DestinationDecoderExp.svg" alt="Wireframes or Process"
            class="w-full rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-900/10" />
          <figcaption class="text-center text-sm text-slate-500 mt-4">Description of the interface, process, or
            component library shown above.</figcaption>
        </figure>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mt-16">The Solution</h2>
        <p>Showcase the final designs, the UI components, motion design elements, and how the system scaled. Highlight
          specific features that drove success and how you collaborated with engineering to make it a reality.</p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mt-16">The Impact</h2>
        <p>Conclude with measurable results, business metrics, and key takeaways.</p>
        <ul class="font-medium text-slate-800">
          <li>Generated $14.9M in Gross Profit.</li>
          <li>Drove 1.48M new app installs.</li>
          <li>Surpassed annual growth targets by 148%.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Siguiente Proyecto -->
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-24 border-t border-slate-200 pt-10 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-slate-400 mb-4">Up Next</p>
        <a href="#" class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 hover:text-brand transition-colors">Elevating Design
          Excellence & Ops &rarr;</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>